Description: Provides exact compound-Poisson simulation and maximum likelihood estimation for the Merton (1976) log-normal jump-diffusion model and the Kou (2002) double-exponential jump-diffusion model.
      A unified S4 class hierarchy exposes calibrate(), simulate(), and
      diagnostic methods for both models. All examples run offline using 
      the included synthetic data generator.
